{
  "stem": "22734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then the train stopped, whether it took two days, one day, three days, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I really wouldn't know, because time stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the-- they unlocked the wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there were such strange figures running around the platform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were all in blue and white stripes with sort of French berets also on their heads, blue and white stripes and high boots.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And everywhere was snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And wherever you looked, in spite of that it was a war and that there was-- had been, you know, the-- no lights, because of planes, you know-- that's what we were told.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It had to be properly-- you shouldn't-- in Theresien, you couldn't even have a tiny, tiny, tiny sign of light.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Everything had to be blacked out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here there were miles upon miles of barbed wire with lights on them, and watchtowers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And dogs were barking everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But mostly the lights amazed me, that I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody asked the guys who spoke Polish who were running around the platform and screaming in German, alles raus, alles raus, everybody out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somebody asked, where are we?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this Polish guy said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he made like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So then, alles raus, alles [GERMAN], everything has to be left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You just get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they put us into some sort of barracks where there were showers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, take off your clothes, have a shower, and put on the clothes that were hanging on the ot-- in the other room and leave your clothes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you lost all your clothes, your shoes, your everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were rags that you put on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they said, men separate, women separate, and-- I think that for us they brought trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
